Introduction

HYNN is a South Korean singer-songwriter under BOD Entertainment and New Order Entertainment. She was a contestant on Superstar K 2016 where she finished in the top 3. She made her solo debut on December 28, 2018 with the digital single "Let Me Out". In 2022, she became a member of the project girl group WSG Wannabe.
